description: City : Winston-Salem, NCD’s Cakes in a Cup & More, LLC is a North Carolina inspected and certified home bakery specializing in cupcakes and cake pops.We create custom cupcakes for special occasions, including, weddings, family reunions, corporate events and more. Our menu will also feature cheesecakes, cakes and cobblers. All products are made fresh to order and from scratch.Come try one of our cupcakes today!
name: D's Cakes In A Cup
